query: INSERT INTO driver_list (racing_number, reference, first_name, last_name, full_name, broadcast_name, tla, country_code, team_name, team_color) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?) ON CONFLICT (racing_number) DO UPDATE SET reference = ?, first_name = ?, last_name = ?, full_name = ?, broadcast_name = ?, tla = ?, country_code = ?, team_name = ?, team_color = ?
